{"tid":1926482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同街站藍屍瘋狂辯論","createTime":"2020-03-15T07:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T14:39:29.000Z","uid":129202,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"277d83c7a26bc2091a47e171cc1c66f352a84e4e","tid":1926482,"uid":129202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7My7GT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7My7GT.jpg&h=6a0596f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWTtWAh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWTtWAh.jpg&h=7beade63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說頭先行過23條街站<br />\n有伯伯叫我簽名<br />\n<br />\n伯伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：請支持23條立法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：因為有外國勢力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：邊個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：下刪2萬字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呀叔你愛國嗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：那為什麼不說普通話<br />\n來 我地抵齊大叫<br />\n「愛國要講普通話」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：靜過大空<br />\n<br />\n（在場藍屍無一個跟住講）<br />\n<br />\n此時便衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兇我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔系香港人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你想攪獨立？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此時我再大叫「愛國要講普通話」<br />\n<br />\n大家無人敢叫<br />\n<br />\n如遇到23條立法藍屍<br />\n<br />\n1.要橋騎劫活動 要比佢地更藍<br />\n2.大聲叫 叫到佢地無面為止<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無得唸"},{"pid":"f06507e1410326f6cf90384aad4c02b2d053b508","tid":1926482,"uid":157994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"有 加速主義"},{"pid":"01638e6487261b9239350579f1fd0320cf99c575","tid":1926482,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"秘密警察真係要c"},{"pid":"e2e27cb16f1a405f93cb793d6112e2da72d62a7e","tid":1926482,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad01bbd0ea72842ebdc15f4bfb23fbe32dae4d7","tid":1926482,"uid":9564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:05:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你影</span></span>"},{"pid":"63790b89143103c068b8fbb457d170ca634ab5b9","tid":1926482,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:06:46.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe5b906d35b1164fba6bd4388a30b0e5e0e71c2","tid":1926482,"uid":16775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:07:17.000Z","msg":"但後生係原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾愛國都會話你搞事"},{"pid":"7f38294c456238b42d1629bd3a09e79946fea42a","tid":1926482,"uid":36702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"樓主好似有啲料到"},{"pid":"07ac10ce229ccfb30f11a5d4e219819cb27a37d9","tid":1926482,"uid":261773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n